                    Eventos de Empresas y Celebraciones Corporativas
                </h2>
                <hr class="w-24 border-t-2 border-border" />
                <p class="max-w-md text-lg text-zinc-300">
                    Conecta con tu equipo en un espacio que inspira
                    productividad y confianza. Nuestro salón se adapta a todas
                    las necesidades corporativas. Ya sea para una jornada formal
                    o una celebración, contarás con:
                </p>
                <div class="flex space-x-4">
                    <button
                        data-slot="button"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&_svg]:pointer-events-none [&_svg:not([class*='size-'])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-xs hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 rounded-md px-6 has-[>svg]:px-4"
                    >
                        Get Started
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="24"
                            height="24"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="lucide lucide-arrow-right"
                            ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </button>
                    <button
                        data-slot="button"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&_svg]:pointer-events-none [&_svg:not([class*='size-'])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive border bg-background shadow-xs hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground dark:bg-input/30 dark:border-input dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-10 rounded-md px-6 has-[>svg]:px-4"
                    >
                        Learn More
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-8">
                <div
                    class="rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-3xl p-6 shadow-sm transition-all"
                >
                    <div
                        class="mb-4 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10"
                    >
                        <VideoIcon className="h-4 w-4" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">
                        Proyector multimedia
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-200">
                        Pantalla gigante para presentaciones y videos, con
                        proyector multimedia de alta definición
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-3xl p-6 shadow-sm transition-all"
                >
                    <div
                        class="mb-4 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10"
                    >
                        <Volume2 className="h-4 w-4" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">
                        Amplificación de sonido
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-200">
                        Sistema de sonido de alta calidad para música y
                        presentaciones en vivo
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-3xl p-6 shadow-sm transition-all"
                >
                    <div
                        class="mb-4 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10"
                    >
                        <Croissant className="h-4 w-4" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">
                        Servicio de coffee break o banquetería
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-200">
                        Servicio de coffee break o banquetería para tus
                        celebraciones y eventos corporativos
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="rounded-lg border border-border/30 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-3xl p-6 shadow-sm transition-all"
                >
                    <div
                        class="mb-4 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10"
                    >
                        <Car className="h-4 w-4" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">
                        Estacionamiento privado y seguro
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-200">
                        Estacionamiento privado y seguro para más de 100
                        vehículos
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
